  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-07-23",
    "date": "2026-02-27T19:58:49Z",
    "text": "Bill to Outlaw Wounding of Official Working Animals Act or the BOWOW Act\n\nThis bill establishes that a\u00a0non-U.S. national (alien under federal law) convicted of, or who admits to having committed, an offense related to harming animals used in law enforcement is inadmissible and deportable."
  },
